      "side": 1,
      "message": "[Major] Line 2668: `presenceManager_-\u003erefresh()` is now called on every connectivity change, including transitions where the account/DHT is not yet connected. That can re-run the same listen attempts while disconnected, causing the same silent failures and unnecessary work during network flaps. Gate this to the connected/registered state, or invoke it from the point where DHT connectivity is confirmed restored.\n```suggestion\n    if (presenceManager_ \u0026\u0026 isRegistered())\n        presenceManager_-\u003erefresh();\n```",
